# @sfcr/notebook-core

- Notebook schema, parsing, validation, and document transforms belong here.
- Forbidden: React, Vite, vitest, imports from `web`, `components/`, `hooks/`.
- After edits: `pnpm --filter @sfcr/notebook-core run check:boundaries`.
- Schema file: `src/sfcr-notebook.schema.json`. Also update `packages/web/public/sfcr-notebook.schema.json` when the public contract changes.
- Package has no runtime vitest suite; behavior is covered via web tests and boundary checks.
